Text: Looks like its pretty good quality. Amazed to see such a good telesync out so soon.
This is the same copy that got a A=4 V=5, so I doubt it is as good as those screens look.
A/V is pretty damn good.  Audio sync is on point til about the 1 hour mark, after that i set it to -190 ms and that was close enough for me.
Do not download and seed, just got a copyright infringement letter on this file!!
